{"metadata":{"name":"Sunan Ibn Majah","section":{"7":{"eng-name":"Fasting","ara-name":"كتاب الصيام"}},"section_detail":{"7":{"hadithnumber_first":1638,"hadithnumber_last":1782,"arabicnumber_first":1638,"arabicnumber_last":1782}}},"hadiths":[{"hadithnumber":1725,"arabicnumber":1725,"text":"حدثنا اسحاق بن منصور، انبانا ابو داود، حدثنا شيبان، عن عاصم، عن زر، عن عبد الله بن مسعود، قال: قلما رايت رسول الله صلى الله عليه وسلم يفطر يوم الجمعة","grades":[{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Hasan"},{"name":"Muhammad Fouad Abd al-Baqi","grade":"Hasan"},{"name":"Shuaib Al Arnaut","grade":"Hasan"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Isnaad Hasan"}],"reference":{"book":7,"hadith":88},"chapter":{"id":37,"ara-name":"باب فِي صِيَامِ يَوْمِ الْجُمُعَةِ","eng-name":"Fasting on a Friday","isFirstHadith":false}}]}